ZH: 1. 我们必须一起抚养孩子。
EN: We must raise the children together.
ZH: 2. 父母的责任是抚养孩子成长。
EN: It is the responsibility of parents to raise children.
ZH: 3. 她抚养了两个狗，而不是养孩子。
EN: She raises two dogs instead of having children.
ZH: 4. 这个项目旨在帮助贫困家庭抚养孩子。
EN: This project aims to assist impoverished families in raising their children.
ZH: 5. 这个组织提供适当的抚养指导。
EN: This organization provides proper parenting guidance.
ZH: 6. 他们抚养了一个聪明又有教养的女儿。
EN: They have raised a smart and well-mannered daughter.
ZH: 7. 她经历了一段艰难的时间，独自抚养她的孩子。
EN: She went through a difficult time, raising her child alone.
ZH: 8. 抚养孩子需要付出很多精力和时间。
EN: Raising a child requires a lot of energy and time.
ZH: 9. 孤儿需要得到适当的抚养和关爱。
EN: Orphans need to receive proper care and nurturing.
ZH: 10. 爷爷奶奶抚养了他们的外孙女。
EN: The grandparents raised their granddaughter.
ZH: 11. 这个家庭以柔和的方式抚养他们的孩子。
EN: This family raises their children in a gentle manner.
ZH: 12. 成为父母的责任是抚养孩子的身心健康。
EN: The duty of being a parent is to raise the child's physical and mental well-being.
ZH: 13. 她决定独自抚养孩子，而不需要任何帮助。
EN: She decided to raise the child alone without any help.
ZH: 14. 这个村子很团结，大家一起抚养孩子。
EN: This village is close-knit, everyone helps in raising the children together.
ZH: 15. 这个孩子是一个优秀的家庭环境抚养成的。
EN: This child was raised in an excellent family environment.
ZH: 16. 父母的责任不仅仅是抚养孩子，还要教育他们。
EN: The responsibility of parents is not only to raise their children but also to educate them.
ZH: 17. 这个计划是为了支持单亲妈妈抚养孩子。
EN: This program is designed to support single mothers in raising their children.
ZH: 18. 哥哥很小的时候就开始抚养弟弟。
EN: The older brother started taking care of the younger brother at a very young age.
ZH: 19. 他们付出了很多努力来抚养他们的孩子得到最好的教育。
EN: They put in a lot of effort to ensure their children receive the best education.
ZH: 20. 这位父亲悄悄地摸摸孩子的头，表达着对他的抚养之爱。
EN: The father gently touched the child's head, expressing his love through nurturing.
